Package: spatialcompare
Type: Package
Title: Visual Tableaux to Compare Spatial Features
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Toby", "Wilkinson", email = "open@tobywilkinson.co.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4905-0522"))
URL: https://tcwilkinson.github.io/spatialcompare, https://github.com/tcwilkinson/spatialcompare
BugReports: https://github.com/tcwilkinson/spatialcompare/issues
Description: Support to construct side-by-side tableaux ("infographics") of diverse spatial 
   features, especially polygons. Projected spatial dimensions are preserved. 
   Possible applications include visualization and comparison of dimensions of ancient and 
   modern cities, or scientific study regions.
